summary: Do youself a favor and go watch Captain Marvel!
body:
Do youself a favor and go watch Captain Marvel!

I’ve waited 4 years for Captain Marvel, I’ve followed the process of the movie being made since it was first announced and now l’ve finally seen it and loved it!!! They changed a lot from the origin story but l knew they were gonna do that and it was still awesome! I CANNOT fucking wait to see her in Avengers Endgame fighting against Thanos, desroying his ass and bonding with the other Avengers! She is a force to be reckoned with!
